Recurrence of pulmonary intravascular bronchoalveolar tumor with mediastinal 
metastasis 20 years later.

Chen TM(1), Donington J, Mak G, Berry GJ, Ruoss SJ, Rosen GD, Upadhyay D.

Author information:
