Pulmonary intravascular bronchoalveolar tumor (IVBAT) also recognized as 
pulmonary epithelioid hemangioendothelioma, is a rare malignant vascular tumor 
of unknown etiology. IVBAT is a tumor of multicentric origin and the lungs are 
rarely involved, with only about 60 cases of pulmonary IVBAT described in the 
